Here's a BST in Python:

```
class Node:
    def __init__(self, value):
        self.left = None
        self.right = None
        self.value = value

def insert(root, value):
    if root is None:
        return Node(value)
    if value < root.value:
        root.left = insert(root.left, value)
    else:
        root.right = insert(root.right, value)
    return root

root = None
root = insert(root, 10)
root = insert(root, 5)
root = insert(root, 20)
```

